1. *Ocu* da kupim nove patike. (I want to buy new shoes.)
2. *Ocu* da odem na izlet. (I want to go on a trip.)
3. *Oce* li biti lepog vremena? (Will the weather be nice?)
4. On *oci* za mene. (He is coming for me.)
5. *Ocima* je gledao kroz prozor. (He looked through the window with his eyes.)
6. *Oce* li da dovedem prijatelja? (Shall I bring a friend?)
7. Ona *oci* da me pozdravi. (She came to greet me.)
8. *Ocu* da dam dobar primer. (I want to set a good example.)